TITLE: Implementing RPC Pattern with RPCRedisBroker
DESCRIPTION: Example usage of RPCRedisBroker for implementing a caller and responder using Redis. The caller makes an RPC call, and the responder processes the call and sends a reply.
SOURCE: https://github.com/discordjs/discord.js/blob/main/packages/brokers/README.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
